These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, juice
1. Beverage:juice is on the far left or far right##3
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Beverage:juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | juice | hot-chocolate |

 #################################
 
